settings.heading: What is raw pet food nutrition?
settings.row_content: Raw pet food nutrition is based on the philosophy that pets thrive best on a diet that mimics what their ancestors ate in the wild. This may include high-quality proteins, vegetables, seeds, nuts and fruits.

settings.heading: Is raw food safe for my pet?
settings.row_content: Yes, when handled and prepared correctly, raw food is safe for your pets. At Harley's, we ensure all our raw products are prepared in a hygienic environment with stringent quality control.

settings.heading: Why should I feed my pet raw food?
settings.row_content:
Just as we humans thrive on fresh food, so do our pets, because food is fuel to the body.

Kibbles, the dry food pellets you can usually get at your favorite commercial pet store, are most often cooked in ultra high temperatures of 90 degrees celsius + (that's only the minimum!)

This high heat causes the alteration and damage in the food's nutritional value, making it difficult for your pet's body to process. Preservatives are also added to lengthen the shelf life of these kibbles, hence making it even harder for your pet's digestive system.

Luckily, there is a better way to feed your pets! Feeding raw provides your pet with food in its most digestible state and at Harley’s, we're here to provide quality nutrition your pets deserve with the convenience you need.

settings.heading: How does a raw diet benefit my pet?
settings.row_content:
When your pet is getting all the nutrients they need, it will show visibly through their bodies.

A raw diet can offer several benefits including improved digestion and absorption, healthier skin and shinier coats, reduced allergy symptoms, stronger teeth, fresher breath, strengthened immune system and more energy.

However, each pet is unique, and results can vary.

settings.heading: Is raw food suitable for all breeds and ages?
settings.row_content:
Yes, raw food can be suitable for pets of all breeds and life stages. However, it's essential to ensure the diet is balanced and meets the nutritional needs of your pet's specific life stage and health condition.

At Harley’s, we make sure to follow the NRC standards to meet the nutrient requirements for all life stages.

Our Story

settings.text:
At Harley's, our story is deeply rooted in love, compassion, and the unwavering devotion of a passionate pet parent.

Our founder, Kathleen Chiang Co, knows all too well the heart-wrenching pain of losing a beloved pet far too soon. Fueled by this personal experience and a steadfast determination to help pets live healthier, happier lives, Harley's was born.

Our mission is to provide the best possible nutrition to pets in the Philippines, and we understand the critical role that proper nutrition plays in the well-being of our furry companions. With a carefully curated selection of the highest quality raw pet food, treats, and supplements, we're here to help you nourish your pets with the love and care they deserve.

As fellow pet lovers, we warmly invite you to join us on this journey of nurturing the health and happiness of our cherished four-legged family members. Together, we can create a brighter, more vibrant future for them, one wholesome meal at a time.
